Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.4.1
====================================
* Fix perf xorg memory calculation
* Fix xdbe property
* Disable by default decoration plugin

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.4.0
====================================
* Avoid damage overflow
* New lightweight build without gtk
* Remove all deprecated features
* Add vblank support
* Optimize shadow plugin

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.3.4
====================================
* Stopping magic mushroom and really fix timeout interval

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.3.3
====================================
* Fix timeout interval calculation
* Fix vblank sync
* Depends from vala-0.18

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.3.2
====================================
* Improve timeout interval delay calculation
* Fix refresh rate detection and vblank sync

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.3.1
====================================

* Port to vala-0.16
* Send ICCM event notification on CCM start/stop (based from Gianpiero patch)
* Fix on screen resize
* Fix screen refresh lookup
* Add auto-refresh and to sync to vblank options
* Update license to LGPL v3
* Add stats plugin
* Code cleanup
* Enhance video memory footprint.
* Add keyboard navigation in Mosaic Mode (close FS#39)
* Clone plugin improvements
* Some bug fixes and small performance enhancement

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.3.0
====================================

* Fix some crash and performances improvements

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.98
====================================

* Fix some crash and performances improvements

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.97
