* Some performances improvements
* Rewrite plugin options load
* Fix root background setting
* Fix fake blur
* Add window animation plugin
* Fix vala support
* Fix clone plugin

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.96
====================================

* Some performances improvements
* Fix some crash
* Add experimental screen clone.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.95
====================================

* Some performances improvements
