Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.94
====================================

* Fix window shade issue
* Some performance improvements
* Add session management support

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.93
====================================

* Fix opacity when set with transset on framed window.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.92
====================================

* Add settings UI page for plugins except magnifier
* Add cursor redirect paint API
* Fix some death window steal on screen
* Mosaic plugin click on window activate it, shadow window when cursor is not
  over them.
* Magnifier plugin use latest cursor redirect API to draw pointer.
* Fix some crash on enable/disable ccm
* Fix some memery leak.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.91
====================================

* Add xdg key configuration files
* Enable by default xdg key configuration files
* Fix some glitches when window return from fullscreen.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.90
====================================

* API cleanup
* Add decoration plugin
* Add snapshot plugin
* Add vala bindings
* Fix shadow plugins
* Fix mosaic plugins
* Add experimental automate plugin
* Add vala plugin sample
* Various fixes

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.2
====================================

* API cleanup.
* Fix TFP mode.
* Magnifier performance improvement.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.1
====================================

* Xrender performance improvement.
* Plugin shadow fix with glitz tfp.
* Glitz tfp backend fixes.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.2.0
====================================

* Stack check rewrite.
* Get/Set image rewrite
* Plugins methods call improvement.
* Timeline support.
* Async property support.
* Dynamic preferences change support.
* Many performances improvements.
* Add magnifier plugin.
* Add mosaic plugin.
* Experimental glitz TFP backend.
* Experimental openvg backend.

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.1.3
====================================

* Add pixmap buffered surface, improve significantly the performance
* Native pixmap backend (for now only xrender backend is supported)
* Fix some issues in shadow plugins.
* Some performances improvements

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.1.2
====================================

* Fix crash on plugin order (fix #04, #05)
* Fix no shm mode
* Animation enhancement
* Fix configuration load and some default value
* Sort extension to ensure they are in good place
* Use region instead rectangle for damage
* Fix freeze plugin and enable it by default
* Add tray icon launcher
* Add menu-animation plugin
* Some performance improvements

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.1.1
====================================

* Don't shadow window without decoration
* Rework of track damage
* Add fade plugin
* Fix some glitches on open and close windows
* Add embrionic freeze plugin
* Add backend support per screen
* Implement CopySubBuffer in glitz backend.
* Detect if an another composite manager run on startup
* Add frame extends support
* Add child window support
* Some performance improvements

Overview of Changes in Cairo Composite Manager 0.1.0
====================================

* First release!

